PortGroup           active_variants 1.1
PortGroup           meson 1.0

name                libgedit-gtksourceview
version             299.2.1
revision            0
license             GPL-2.0+
description         Gedit Technology - Source code editing widget gtk3+
long_description    libgedit-gtksourceview is part of Gedit Technology. \
                    libgedit-gtksourceview is a library that extends GtkTextView, the standard GTK \
                    widget for multiline text editing. This library adds support for syntax \
                    highlighting, undo/redo, file loading and saving, search and replace, a \
                    completion system, printing, displaying line numbers, and other features typical \
                    of a source code editor. Targets Gtk3
categories          gnome
maintainers         {christophecvr @christophecvr}
platforms           darwin
homepage            https://gitlab.gnome.org/World/gedit/libgedit-gtksourceview
